### The Chicken Of The Cave

There's a pretty funny scene in [Anchorman 2](http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0462712/?ref_=tt_cl_t4) where washed-up sports anchor Champ Kind defends his choice to pass fried bat as fried chicken in his restaurant by calling bats the “chicken of the cave”:

